{"tid":626032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"牙朗：今天學習到很多 一步一步來","createTime":"2018-04-11T23:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T00:58:16.000Z","uid":25345,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c91546304f2bc27837ef84374ac6243003cf9303","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:37:46.000Z","msg":"皇馬在歐冠1/4決賽次回合主場1比3不敵尤文，但仍以總比分4-3淘汰對手晉級半決賽。賽後在接受媒體采訪時，C羅表示，最後時刻確確實實是個點球，稱自己不明白尤文球員為什麽還要抗議。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n關於本場比賽，C羅說：&ldquo;我們確確實實遇到了極大的困難，但是通過這場比賽我們可以學到很多。在足球場上，沒有什麽東西是送給你的，任何時候都要戰鬥到最後一刻。今天皇馬本可以有機會取得更多進球，但是尤文的防線和布馮的發揮太好了，我們很被動。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n對於最後時刻的點球，葡萄牙人說：&ldquo;那確確實實是個點球，我不理解為什麽尤文圖斯的球員還要極力抗議。他們確實從背後對巴斯克斯犯規了，如果沒有犯規的話，那應該是個進球。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n同時C羅表示，自己罰點球時很冷靜：&ldquo;雖然都是噓聲，但是我很冷靜，我知道進球已經是命中註定的了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n最後，談到半決賽時，葡萄牙人表示：&ldquo;一步一步來，足球場上可以發生任何事情，我們先要從這場比賽中好好學習。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"b5524fdd5ff29672ebfa4dcbdf3c8bae1b570bc9","tid":626032,"uid":3194,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:39:12.000Z","msg":"雖然都是噓聲，但是我很冷靜，我知道進球已經是命中註定的了<br />\n<br />\n好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3abb5aeee39260f08b7ad0af0a2c45a672feca","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"C羅透露：&ldquo;罰點球之前，我的心跳加速，但我讓自己平靜下來，因為我知道，這是具有決定性的。感謝上帝，我罰入點球，我們晉級了！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0666456cb4333e4062719fccc3920893c985f7da","tid":626032,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3abb5aeee39260f08b7ad0af0a2c45a672feca","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"C羅透露：&ldquo;罰點球之前，我的心跳加速，但我讓自己平靜下來，因為我知道，這是具有決定性的。感謝上帝，我罰入點球，我們晉級了！&rdquo;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"感謝足球上帝美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97bde321b4408b5efc0e74969d2703bb6282318","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"0666456cb4333e4062719fccc3920893c985f7da","tid":626032,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3abb5aeee39260f08b7ad0af0a2c45a672feca","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"C羅透露：&ldquo;罰點球之前，我的心跳加速，但我讓自己平靜下來，因為我知道，這是具有決定性的。感謝上帝，我罰入點球，我們晉級了！&rdquo;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"感謝足球上帝美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/074736_b2333198e160e7b452adc958b2373252.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F074736_b2333198e160e7b452adc958b2373252.png&h=0090be25&s={SIZE}\" />上帝發出光芒"},{"pid":"405317f191c41acceb1c8c4fad9bbf75b67ca84a","tid":626032,"uid":52123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b5524fdd5ff29672ebfa4dcbdf3c8bae1b570bc9","tid":626032,"uid":3194,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:39:12.000Z","msg":"雖然都是噓聲，但是我很冷靜，我知道進球已經是命中註定的了<br />\n<br />\n好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:50:59.000Z","msg":"贏左真係講乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625aa34c9359bceecf24d5abce550beb6bc447f2","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c97bde321b4408b5efc0e74969d2703bb6282318","tid":626032,"uid":25345,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"0666456cb4333e4062719fccc3920893c985f7da","tid":626032,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3abb5aeee